    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "e93355cd-de03-40d0-b43c-333df28e369d",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "d2316d52-77c4-465a-9a79-37b5c25071a9",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "3",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "2c7a172b-56d2-4866-8aed-c271280d98c9",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "For this class, we shall be devising and enchanting Incendia runestones. These Combat runestones, once activated, create a small area of magical fire. This fire will continue to burn until the caster retrieves the runestone.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "95d4eb00-36e7-402b-bf57-bb2bf73b0750",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "This runestone consumes a great deal of energy, and so requires the expenditure of a large amount of Mojo when you activate it. Of all the runestones we create for this class, Incendia is the most costly to use.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "d4770464-897b-4c4a-90f9-c1aecea2fbd4",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Nevertheless, it has a great deal of versatility. The flames do magical damage to the creature that activates it. It affects both corporal and noncorporal Undead. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "869cadb3-e720-4b23-b872-10b8beb7abc3",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "And most sentient creatures have the instinct to avoid flames, so the runestone can act as a temporary barrier.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "ad146b12-3fbf-455f-a5ea-6cb8acabdb2e",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "Are there any questions or commentary before we get started, Mr. O'Conner?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "114a7292-a7fe-40df-bbfe-f3078532fc9c",
                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                    "skill": "Magic",
                    "amount": "5",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "2fe566e8-33f0-445f-bc9f-48ea90d333be",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "ccaec671-2345-4546-9927-e323cf533955",
                            "text": "Compliment the Professor",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "9b2dc5a5-aa72-42b7-83c5-d56e9c6cdf9a",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "I just wanted to say that you make these lectures and lessons fascinating... I just want to close my eyes and savor your words.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "168e4f76-2234-456c-b355-7020ada7d2fb",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I have noticed in the past that you do a great deal of <i>savoring</i> in this class. That is fine - as long as your snoring does not become too distracting.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "b48fab0a-306a-4d4b-b148-1e49f94c3c03",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "64",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "770e6652-52cb-4a4b-b9fb-f5430d59068a",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
